}}
Infoboxes already reduce text size to 88%, and [[:en:MOS:FONTSIZE|MOS:FONTSIZE]] sets a lower limit for text size at 85% of the normal page font size, so it is not appropriate to use font size reduction when this template is used in an infobox. The example here is produced by:
